Over half a million protesters gathered in and around Tahrir Suqare, Cairo by local time 1PM, with numbers reaching over one million by 2PM. Hundreds of thousands of protesters have gathered also in Sidi Gaber, Alexandria. 250,000 protesters have gathered also in Suez. 250,000 protesters have gathered also in El Arish.
